        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 36–44. New records of Cerambycidae deposited at UNIR: 36, Hydraschema leptostylum Lane, 1938; 37, Trigonopeplus bispecularis White, 1855; 38, Bebelis picta Pascoe, 1875; 39, Ischioloncha wollastonii Thomson, 1860; 40, Drycothaea angustifrons (Breuning, 1943); 41, Graminea hispida Galileo & Martins, 1990; 42, Colobothea styligera Bates, 1865; 43, Desmiphora (Desmiphora) fasciculata (Fabricius, 1792); 44, Taeniotes orbignyi Guérin-Méneville, 1844." ;
